Lightspeed, watches the two leave, than realizes he should report to 
his leader. "I'll be back, but I need to report to the other 
Technobots, plus Ironhide wanted to see us" and he walked out of the 
ship, before transforming into his car mode, and quickly accelerating 
to 400mph for a few short seconds, then back to 300mph, and heads 
away.

OOC: Okay guys, I wont be back until monday, but none of my 
characters should need to post until then anyways. Seee ya :)
